    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How to Fund Your Wallet with SOL to Play Star Atlas" class="article-title">
          How to Fund Your Wallet with SOL to Play Star Atlas
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:17:24Z" title="2025-12-08T18:17:24Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:17</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47061467575571-How-to-Fund-Your-Wallet-with-SOL-to-Play-Star-Atlas/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>To start playing Star Atlas, especially in browser-based experiences like SAGE Labs, you'll need a small amount of <strong>SOL</strong> (Solana) in your wallet to pay for transaction fees.</p><p>Whether you’re brand new to crypto or already familiar with other blockchains, this guide will walk you through two ways to add SOL to your wallet.</p><h3 id="h_01KBJQWVS83QBARMR2YFV6B48K">Option 1: Buy SOL on a Centralized Exchange (CEX)</h3><p>You can purchase SOL using a credit card or bank transfer on a major centralized exchange (CEX), then send the tokens to your Solana wallet.</p><p><strong>Popular CEXs that support SOL:</strong></p><ul>
<li><p><a href="https://backpack.exchange" target="_new" rel="noopener">Backpack Exchange</a></p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://coinbase.com" target="_new" rel="noopener">Coinbase</a></p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://binance.com" target="_new" rel="noopener">Binance</a></p></li>
<li><p>Kraken, OKX, Bybit, and many more...</p></li>
</ul><p><strong>Steps:</strong></p><ol>
<li><p>Sign up and verify your identity (KYC) on your chosen exchange.</p></li>
<li><p>Buy <strong>SOL</strong> using your preferred payment method.</p></li>
<li><p>Go to your Solana wallet (e.g. Phantom, Backpack, Solflare).</p></li>
<li><p>Copy your wallet address.</p></li>
<li><p>Withdraw SOL from the exchange to your wallet address.</p></li>
</ol><p>📌 <em><em>Make sure to double-check that you're using a Solana-compatible wallet address.</em></em></p><h3 id="h_01KBJQWVS8Y8TR1R7RH79EA4G7">Option 2: Buy SOL Directly with a Credit Card via <strong>Topper</strong>
</h3><p>If you don’t want to register on an exchange, you can <strong>buy SOL directly with a credit or debit card</strong> using <strong>Topper</strong>, which is integrated into the Star Atlas website.<img class="wysiwyg-image-resized" style="aspect-ratio: 826/365; width: 74.35%;" src="/hc/article_attachments/47065279859731" width="826" height="365"></p><h3 id="h_01KBJQRS6F17W83KJKT3VX9GFV">How to Use Topper:</h3><ol>
<li><p>Visit <a href="https://play.staratlas.com" target="_new" rel="noopener">play.staratlas.com</a> and connect your wallet.</p></li>
<li><p>Click the wallet icon in the bottom left.</p></li>
<li><p>Scroll to <strong>Manage your wallet’s fund</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Launch</strong> next to <strong>Topper</strong>.</p>
<p><img class="wysiwyg-image-resized" style="aspect-ratio: 535/849; width: 34.04%;" src="/hc/article_attachments/47065279864339" width="535" height="849"></p>
</li>
</ol><p>A popup will appear. Then:</p><ul>
<li><p>Select your currency (USD, EUR, etc.).</p></li>
<li><p>Choose <strong>SOL</strong> as the token you want to receive.</p></li>
<li><p>Enter the amount you want to spend.</p></li>
<li><p>Sign in or create an account with Uphold.</p></li>
<li><p>Complete identity verification (KYC).</p></li>
<li><p>Add your card and confirm your purchase.</p></li>
</ul><p>Once completed, the SOL will be sent directly to your wallet.</p></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

